answers.body_markdown:
You have defined to use the [parent with version 2.6.6][1]. Then you add dependencies for other components
which you like to use for example `spring-boot-starter-security`. In Spring boot the basic 
idea is to use the components which are offered by the spring team. This means you should simply
define a component like the following: 

&lt;!-- language:language-xml --&gt;

    &lt;dependencies&gt;
      ...
      &lt;dependency&gt;
        &lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;
        &lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-starter-security&lt;/artifactId&gt;
      &lt;/dependency&gt;    
      ..
    &lt;/dependencies&gt;
      

Pay attention to the point that here no version is given. This means based on the parent,
the version is used which is given through the parent. This means you are using the following
artifact [`org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-dependencies:2.6.6`][2] which contains all
components (usually defined by starters). For example `spring-boot-starter-thymeleaf`
which should be used like this:

&lt;!-- language:language-xml --&gt;

    &lt;dependencies&gt;
      ...
      &lt;dependency&gt;
        &lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;
        &lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-starter-thymeleaf&lt;/artifactId&gt;
      &lt;/dependency&gt;    
      ..
    &lt;/dependencies&gt;

But in contradiction to the idea you have used the starters, but unfortunately you have
defined also a versions like this:

&lt;!-- language:language-xml --&gt;

    &lt;dependencies&gt;
      &lt;dependency&gt;
        &lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;
        &lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-starter-security&lt;/artifactId&gt;
        &lt;version&gt;2.3.3.RELEASE&lt;/version&gt;
      &lt;/dependency&gt;
      &lt;dependency&gt;
        &lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;
        &lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-starter-thymeleaf&lt;/artifactId&gt;
        &lt;version&gt;2.5.2&lt;/version&gt;
      &lt;/dependency&gt;
          ..
    &lt;/dependencies&gt;

The given versions are different from the version of your used parent which should in sync. 
Technically you can do that manually like this:

&lt;!-- language:language-xml --&gt;

    &lt;dependencies&gt;
      &lt;dependency&gt;
        &lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;
        &lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-starter-security&lt;/artifactId&gt;
        &lt;version&gt;2.6.6&lt;/version&gt;
      &lt;/dependency&gt;
      &lt;dependency&gt;
        &lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;
        &lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-starter-thymeleaf&lt;/artifactId&gt;
        &lt;version&gt;2.6.6&lt;/version&gt;
      &lt;/dependency&gt;
          ..
    &lt;/dependencies&gt;

But the easiest way (makes maintenance easier) is to omit the version. That in consequence
means the version is defined by the parent. This also makes an upgrade of a Spring Boot version
very easy because the only thing you need to change is version of your parent for example 
like this:


&lt;!-- language:language-xml --&gt;

    &lt;parent&gt;
      &lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;
      &lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-starter-parent&lt;/artifactId&gt;
      &lt;version&gt;2.6.7&lt;/version&gt;
      &lt;relativePath/&gt; &lt;!-- lookup parent from repository --&gt;
    &lt;/parent&gt;


You have also defined a component in your `pom.xml` file with a particular version:

&lt;!-- language:language-xml --&gt;

    &lt;dependency&gt;
      &lt;groupId&gt;mysql&lt;/groupId&gt;
      &lt;artifactId&gt;mysql-connector-java&lt;/artifactId&gt;
      &lt;version&gt;8.0.25&lt;/version&gt;
    &lt;/dependency&gt;
    

So in the end your `pom.xml` file should look like this:

&lt;!-- language:language-xml --&gt;

    &lt;project xmlns=&quot;http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0&quot; xmlns:xsi=&quot;http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance&quot; xsi:schemaLocation=&quot;http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0 http://maven.apache.org/maven-v4_0_0.xsd&quot;&gt;
    
    &lt;modelVersion&gt;4.0.0&lt;/modelVersion&gt;
    
      &lt;parent&gt;
        &lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;
        &lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-starter-parent&lt;/artifactId&gt;
        &lt;version&gt;2.6.6&lt;/version&gt;
        &lt;relativePath/&gt; &lt;!-- lookup parent from repository --&gt;
      &lt;/parent&gt;
    
    &lt;groupId&gt;com.example&lt;/groupId&gt;
    &lt;artifactId&gt;heloworld&lt;/artifactId&gt;
    &lt;version&gt;0.0.1-SNAPSHOT&lt;/version&gt;
    &lt;name&gt;heloworld&lt;/name&gt;
    &lt;description&gt;heloworld&lt;/description&gt;
    &lt;packaging&gt;war&lt;/packaging&gt;
    
      &lt;properties&gt;
        &lt;java.version&gt;8&lt;/java.version&gt;
      &lt;/properties&gt;
    
      &lt;dependencies&gt;
        &lt;dependency&gt;
          &lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;
          &lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-starter-web&lt;/artifactId&gt;
        &lt;/dependency&gt;
        &lt;dependency&gt;
          &lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;
          &lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-starter-tomcat&lt;/artifactId&gt;
          &lt;scope&gt;provided&lt;/scope&gt;
        &lt;/dependency&gt;
        &lt;dependency&gt;
          &lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;
          &lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-starter-security&lt;/artifactId&gt;
        &lt;/dependency&gt;
        &lt;dependency&gt;
          &lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;
          &lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-starter-thymeleaf&lt;/artifactId&gt;
        &lt;/dependency&gt;
        &lt;dependency&gt;
          &lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;
          &lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-starter-test&lt;/artifactId&gt;
          &lt;scope&gt;test&lt;/scope&gt;
        &lt;/dependency&gt;
        &lt;dependency&gt;
          &lt;groupId&gt;mysql&lt;/groupId&gt;
          &lt;artifactId&gt;mysql-connector-java&lt;/artifactId&gt;
